<i>Vic-prezidantoj</i>.</li>
<li>S<sup>roj</sup> <span class="sc">Boulet</span>, <span class="sc">Dervaux</span>, <span class="sc">Grabowski</span>, <span class="sc">Kühnl</span>,
<i>Sekretarioj</i>.</li>
</ul>
